  Two paths

  1. Stay on T4, run sequentially. Multi-subject full-size on T4 is roughly
  ~30–45 min/run × 5 = ~3 hr wall. Free, reliable, slow.
  2. Back to A100, run strictly sequentially (one subprocess at a time). ~5–7
  min/run × 5 = ~30 min. The lesson is locked in: never parallel.

  I'd lean toward path 2 unless you've capped A100 budget. Path 1 if cost is the
   dominant concern. Tell me which and I'll launch.

